  "reviewed_at": "2026-07-03",
  "scope": "wave2 fan-out migration: the 2 legacy-parity read streams only; Buzzsprout also exposes write/update endpoints for episodes and podcasts which legacy never implemented (read-only connector) and remain out of scope.",
  "endpoints": [
